'desc': [u'

Remanika Printed Women's Tunic Price: Rs.900

Bring into your casual staples an offbeat style with this tunic from Remanika. For a funky street style
column17: this grey and black tunic has pockets and buttons at the front; the prints too are appealing and give you a snazzy style. The chic belt at the waist lets you get a stylish silhouette while the roll up sleeves add to the groovy air. Crafted from cotton
column18:
this tunic keeps you comfy all day long.

\r\n

\r\n\tOn those mall-hopping and dinner plans on weekends with your soul sisters
column19:
look every bit the smart city lass and sport a charming attitude; team this Remanika Tunic with a pair of skinny jeans and stilettos.

\n
\n ']
